&lt;h2 id=&quot;토마호크-hatchet&quot;&gt;토마호크 (Hatchet)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;근접무기 (Melee Weapon)&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;등급: 비범 (Uncommon)&lt;/li&gt;
